ll knew that.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">They just assumed, Henny especially, that it was a way to keep people from flirting with him. A way to field off those who wanted <em>one thing</em> from the masked Lieutenant.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"sApL7EizwuszgTi7xyX3z.webp","creator":"Ophichus","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🎮 Game","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":5164,"messages":133251,"created_at":"2026-01-23T17:44:50.444329+00:00"}